<DATE_TIME> 1999-09-23 10:00:18 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<CATEGORY> financial </CATEGORY>
<HEADLINE> Big Movers in the Stock Market  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	NEW YORK (AP) -- Stocks that are moving substantially or trading  
heavily today on the New York Stock Exchange and Nasdaq Stock 
Market. 

</P>
<P>
                               *NYSE    	

</P>
<P>
 *Rite Aid Corp., down 2 3/16 at 11 13/16    	
</P>
<P>
	Moody's Investors Service is reviewing the credit rating of Rite  
Aid, citing concerns about the company's weak operating 
profitability and high leverage, as well as uncertainty about its 
future business configuration. 

</P>
<P>
 *Georgia-Pacific Corp., down 4 11/16 at 39 15/16    	
</P>
<P>
	PaineWebber said the paper company may miss third-quarter  
earnings estimates. PaineWebber had previously forecast earnings of 
$1.45 per share. 

</P>
<P>
 *Tektronix Inc., down 3 1/4 at 32 15/16    	
