win in 1992 and only the second in the last 21 years. There have 
been eight raceoffs in the Jug's 54 years. 
</P>
<P>
	Pierce bided his time, holding Blissfull Hall in third or fourth  
place until going wide on the last turn. The Cambest colt, who had 
lost the lead at the same spot an hour earlier in the second heat, 
pulled away down the stretch to win in 1:55 3-5 by a length over 
