<HEADLINE> NFL Sets Attendance Mark for Week 2 </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	NEW YORK (AP) -- The NFL set an all-time weekend attendance  
record last week, attracting more than 1 million fans to games. 
</P>
<P>
