<HEADLINE>  Rescuers Battle Clock in Taiwan </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	TAIPEI, Taiwan (AP) -- As cries for help increasingly turned to  
ominous silence, rescue teams battled the clock today to save 
nearly 2,000 trapped and missing victims of Taiwan's devastating 
earthquake. 
</P>
<P>
