	Textron Financial Corp. plans to acquire Litchfield for $183  
million in cash, or $24.50 a share. Litchfield is a commercial 
finance company specializing in resort and recreation industries. 

</P>
<P>
 *ASI Solutions Inc., down 2 13/32 at 4 23/32    	
</P>
<P>
	ASI, a human resources company, said earnings for its second and  
third quarters will fall below earnings reported in the same 
periods last year. The company said it expects recovery to begin in 
the fourth quarter. 



  	   	
